title: Highland Superstitions Connected with the Druids, Fairies, Witchcraft, Second-Sight, Halloween, Sacred Wells and Lochs
description: This is Reverend Alexander MacGregor's excellent work on the superstitions in the British Highlands, containing chapters about general superstitions, druidism, fairies, witchcraft, second-sight, smaller superstitions, hallowe'en, sacred wells and lochs ...
author: Alexander MacGregor
